               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa taklil “Book of the Marriage Ritual” (fols. 3r-40ra)
 -
                     Prayers on the clothes (fols. 3r-11rb l.10)
 - Prayers on the bride and the
                     bridegroom (fols. 11rb l.11-37va l.15)
 - Order to be read to the bride and
                     the bridegroom (fols. 37va l.15-40rb l.15)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
